\subsection{Models}

\textbf{Mistral-7B-Instruct}~\citep{jiang2023mistral} uses grouped query attention and sliding window attention for efficient inference. Its pretraining is primarily European-centric, which explains its relatively weaker zero-shot performance on non-Latin-script
languages. \\
\textbf{Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct}~\citep{qwen25techreport} was trained on 18T tokens with explicit multilingual coverage, including
Indic scripts. \\
Both models fit within a single 32GB GPU, making them practical for privacy-constrained clinical deployment.

